\par\par \b \uc2  Habibie ready to unveil his 1st  \highlight22\uc2 budget \highlight\uc2  today. \b0\par\par\uc2 534 \uc2 words\par \uc2 5 January 1999\par \uc2 Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par  8 \par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 1999 The Jakarta Post\par \par \uc2  JAKARTA (JP): President B.J. Habibie is set to unveil his first draft \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  to the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2  (DPR) today amid simmering political tensions and a sagging \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  The President is scheduled to address the House plenary session at 10 A.M. to outline the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  for the 1999/2000 \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  year, which begins on April 1. \par \par \uc2  The House will then deliberate the draft \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  and pass it into law. \par \par \uc2  Unlike during the 32-year rule of former president Soeharto, the government is likely to face a challenge from the House before the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  is approved. Under Soeharto, the \b \highlight22\uc2 legislative\b0 \highlight\uc2  body gained notoriety as the government's rubber stamp. \par \par \uc2  The government is expected to allocate considerable sums of money to provide \b \highlight22\uc2 subsidies\b0 \highlight\uc2  in the 1999/2000 \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  under the auspices of the social safety net programs and to assist small-scale entrepreneurs. \par \par \uc2  The government will also disclose the funds it intends to allocate to finance recapitalization of the country's beleaguered banks. \par \par \uc2  Many analysts have predicted that the upcoming \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  will run at a large \b \highlight22\uc2 deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  as the result of depressed oil prices and stunted \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenues generated by the government since the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  sank into recession. \par \par \uc2  In a November report, finance minister Bambang Subianto said that the government would assume a crude oil price of between US$12 and $13 per barrel, a rupiah-U.S. dollar exchange rate of between Rp 7,000 and Rp 8,000, \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  growth between 1 percent and minus 1 percent, and inflation of between 15 percent and 20 when drafting the 1999/2000 \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  Inflation was recorded at 77.63 in 1998. \par \par \uc2  Economist Pande Radja Silalahi of the Center for Strategic and International Studies called on the government and the House to avoid making a major issues of the assumptions used to draft the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  "Assumptions used to calculate the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  must be regarded merely as a guide and prone to changes," Pande told The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2  In 1998, the government was forced to revise the 1998/1999 \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  three times because of the rupiah's roller coaster ride against the dollar. \par \par \uc2  Many have predicted further volatility in the rupiah this year, particularly around two major political events - the general election in June and the subsequent presidential election in November. \par \par \uc2  It is feared that both events could lead to widespread violence and chaos. \par \par \uc2  Pande expressed hope that the government would exercise wisdom and austerity in next year's \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 , pointing out that \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  and political \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  would linger in the country and that a global \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  downturn was also a real possibility. \par \par \uc2  "Unlike in previous \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  years, the degree of \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  will be very high and it will be hard to make precise calculations for the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 ," he told the Post on Monday. \par \par \uc2  Pande warned the government against including populist measures in the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  to improve the political standing of the current administration, which continues to be undermined by its close association to Soeharto. \par \par \uc2  The government should instead focus on revitalizing \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  activities using sound \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  judgment, particularly in the real sector and through the social safety net program, he said. (das) \par \par \uc2  Copyright 1999 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020010906dv15001i6\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
