\par\par \b \uc2  New income  \highlight22\uc2 tax \highlight\uc2  target viewed as unrealistic. \b0\par\par\uc2 693 \uc2 words\par \uc2 7 January 1999\par \uc2 Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par  1 \par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 1999 The Jakarta Post\par \par \uc2  JAKARTA (JP): The government's new income \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  target involving an increase in revenue of more than 57 percent in the 1999/2000 draft \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  amid continuing \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  hardships is seen as unrealistic by economists. \par \par \uc2  Raden Pardede, a senior economist at PT Danareksa Securities, said on Wednesday that the income \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  target was too optimistic in a country plagued by \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  contraction. \par \par \uc2  "The 57 percent increase is unbelievable. A 20 percent increase is more acceptable," Raden told The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2  Sri Mulyani Indrawati from the University of Indonesia agreed and said that the targeted Rp 42.63 trillion (US$5.7 billion) in income \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenue would be difficult to realize. \par \par \uc2  "The revenue from income \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  this \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  year was big enough because of the large contribution from income \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  on bank deposits. This is now difficult to obtain because \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2  have started to drop," Sri said. \par \par \uc2  The benchmark \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  promissory note (SBI) interest rate was boosted to as high as 70 percent per annum in August to help curb inflation and stabilize the exchange rate of the rupiah against the U.S. dollar. \par \par \uc2  But the rate has now dropped to around 35 percent following positive developments in the currency and the inflation rate. \par \par \uc2  Besides falling \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2 , capital flight would also reduce potential revenues from \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  on bank deposit interest income, said Bomer Pasaribu, chairman of the Center for Labor and Development Studies. \par \par \uc2  "The government expects too much from \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  on bank deposit interest income, forgetting that in the current period of \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainties\b0 \highlight\uc2 , big money would not go to local national banks but to Singapore and other safe countries," he said. \par \par \uc2  President B.J. Habibie on Tuesday unveiled the draft of the 1999/2000 State \b \highlight22\uc2 Budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 , in which out of the Rp 140.80 trillion in domestic revenues, more than 50 percent will be derived from income \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  and value-added \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  Revenue from income \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  is set at Rp 40.63 trillion, a 57.2 percent increase from the Rp 25.85 trillion target set in the current 1998/1999 \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  Finance Minister Bambang Subianto expected the 15 percent income \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  from bank time-deposits interest income to continue to be the major contributor of income \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenue. \par \par \uc2  "We will just have to work hard to achieve the target," he told reporters, following Habibie's presentation. \par \par \uc2  He declined to give details. \par \par \uc2  Bomer, expressing skepticism, said: "That's totally over-optimistic. It is impossible to reach that target at a time when we are suffering our worst \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  crisis in decades where corporate income is almost nil." \par \par \uc2  The \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  is foreseen "growing" by zero percent in the 1999/2000 \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  year, which Habibie considered a condition still far from normal. \par \par \uc2  Raden noted that the target for value-added \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  and non-\b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenue from dividends of state-owned companies and proceeds from their privatization was also too optimistic. \par \par \uc2  The government expects to collect Rp 34.7 trillion from value-added and luxury \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2  for the 1999/2000 \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  year's \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 , a 20 percent increase from the current \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  The government, meanwhile, has set a target of income from non-\b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenues of Rp 25.8 trillion, a 3.2 percent drop from this year's \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  Raden, however, was surprised that the government has set a lower foreign revenue target both in the form of program loans and project loans. \par \par \uc2  Foreign-derived revenues are set at Rp 77.40 trillion, which is 32.5 percent lower than the figure in the current \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  Raden suspected that the government had deliberately set a lower foreign revenue target to balance the overly optimistic target it has for \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenues. \par \par \uc2  The government, Raden said, could draw on additional foreign loan sourcing like the Miyazawa Plan and the International Development Assistance, which is now available to the country as it has plunged into the poor nation category. \par \par \uc2  Thus, when the government is able to draw on larger foreign loans, these could be used to compensate for the possible lower realization of domestic revenues, especially from \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  sources, he said. (rei/rid) \par \par \uc2  Copyright 1999 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020010906dv17001n8\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
