\par\par \b \uc2  Experts suggest CPO export  \highlight22\uc2 tax \highlight\uc2  should be reduced to below 15%. \b0\par\par\uc2 514 \uc2 words\par \uc2 25 January 1999\par \uc2 Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par  8 \par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 1999 The Jakarta Post\par \par \uc2  JAKARTA (JP): Leading analysts suggest that the government cut the current 60 percent export \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  on crude palm oil (CPO) to below 15 percent or abolish it altogether to collect more badly needed foreign exchange. \par \par \uc2  Bungaran Saragih of the Bogor Institute of Agriculture said on Saturday that he could understand the maintenance of export \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  on CPO to curb a drastic outflow of the commodity to the overseas market but the \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  should be lower than 15 percent. \par \par \uc2  The government, nevertheless, has planned to cut the current CPO export \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  to no lower than 40 percent. \par \par \uc2  "Lowering the CPO export \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  to 40 percent doesn't make any sense at all. The \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  should be removed, or, if we want to control CPO trading, it should be set no higher than 15 percent, the level which would still attract foreign buyers and encourage farmers to cultivate their oil palms," he told The Jakarta Post from Medan, North Sumatra. \par \par \uc2  Bungaran noted that the current 60 percent export \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  was set in July when the rupiah reached Rp 13,000 to the U.S dollar. \par \par \uc2  The rupiah is now traded at between Rp 8,000 and Rp 9,000 per U.S dollar. With the rupiah at this level, the CPO export \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  should be set at 15 percent. \par \par \uc2  Executive Director of the Center of Agriculture \b \highlight22\uc2 Policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  Studies H.S. Dillon said the government's \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  of maintaining the export \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  on CPO, although the \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  will be cut, is counterproductive to its pledge to adopt a people-oriented \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  Dillon said the high export \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  on CPO and its byproducts had halved the incomes of oil palm farmers as prices for oil palm kernels had dropped sharply. \par \par \uc2  "The high export \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  has adversely affected the welfare of oil palm smallholders and benefited the urban consumers, those who are already rich," Dillon told the Post. \par \par \uc2  Bungaran agreed and said that maintaining a low cooking oil price should not be a top government priority in tackling the 17-month long \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  crisis. \par \par \uc2  "CPO is not an essential commodity. We're not going to starve if we don't consume fried food," he said. \par \par \uc2  Bungaran said the government \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  on imposing a high export \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  on CPO resulted in a 70 percent drop in its export value last year. \par \par \uc2  He said the country would earn at least $2.5 billion from CPO exports this year if the government liberalized the trade. \par \par \uc2  The export value of CPO last year reached only US$420 million, compared to $1.5 billion in 1997, he said. \par \par \uc2  In times of depleting foreign exchange \b \highlight22\uc2 reserves\b0 \highlight\uc2 , the government should actually promote more exports of potential commodities like CPO. \par \par \uc2  Dillon noted that the government's intervention in CPO trading had caused foreign buyers to turn to other CPO producers, especially Malaysia. \par \par \uc2  "Inconsistency in government regulations covering trade in CPO will kill the business in the long term because the international market will view this as increasing risk and \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2 ." (gis) \par \par \uc2  Copyright 1999 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020010906dv1p00291\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
